  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall aim of this study is to disseminate the evidence‐based Connect for Health
      program, specifically targeting pediatric primary care practices that deliver care to
      low‐income children in the US who have a disproportionately high prevalence of childhood
      obesity and evaluate the effectiveness of the program implementation and dissemination.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
